<h2>Best Performing Campaign</h2>



<p>ProfitMetrics has a lot of success with its “Test din ROAS” campaign.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="797" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-1024x797.png" alt="Profitmetrics test din roas" class="wp-image-102653" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-1024x797.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-300x234.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-768x598.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-380x296.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-600x467.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-760x592.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-64x50.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-630x490.png 630w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-220x171.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas-385x300.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-test-din-roas.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>This SleekBox promotes a ROAS calculator and has a conversation rate of 4.86%. Frederik wanted to make it easy for site visitors to calculate their ROAS and see if their paid ads are generating actual profit. Once a visitor has calculated their ROAS, they get the results by email, giving Frederik and ProfitMetrics a really good sales lead. Frederik was also surprised to know that most of his visitors come from desktop because his understanding was that most customers start their journey on mobile.</p>



<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>The Results</h2>



<p>Frederik also wanted to get more demo bookings. We implemented a demo booking popup on the site where visitors can book a demo with Frederik personally. The results so far have been very promising with a conversion rate of 10%.</p>



<p>They recently created an A/B test to see if a top bar&nbsp;<em>without</em>&nbsp;an eBook offer would outperform their slide-in&nbsp;<em>with</em>&nbsp;the eBook offer.</p>



<p>This is the top bar:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="613" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-1024x613.png" alt="Profitmetrics Book Demo" class="wp-image-102645" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-1024x613.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-300x180.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-768x460.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-380x227.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-600x359.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-760x455.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-740x443.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-220x132.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo-385x230.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Profitmetrics-Book-Demo.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Knowing that you need to provide value to get people to sign up for a newsletter, Frederik came up with the idea of offering a valuable resource in exchange for an email address (the resource is called “How to increase your bottom line by 242% without increasing your marketing spend”). We set up a lead generation SleekBox with this offer, which as of writing, has a conversion rate of 3.25%.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="718" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-1024x718.png" alt="ProfitMetrics Lead Generation" class="wp-image-102649" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-1024x718.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-300x210.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-768x538.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-380x266.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-600x421.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-760x533.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-699x490.png 699w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-220x154.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation-385x270.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/ProfitMetrics-Lead-Generation.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>Final Thoughts</h2>



<p>By implementing Sleeknote on their site, ProfitMetrics have been able to better understand what their customers want from their site. It has also given them the opportunity to engage with their customers and provide them with relevant content.</p>


<div id="testimonial-block_5f6352e619ded" class="block-testimonial">
    <blockquote class="quote">
        “I’ve been very satisfied with the outcome of this collaboration. The whole experience has been on my terms, and it has given me the freedom to focus all my energy on growing ProfitMetrics and providing outstanding service to our customers.”    </blockquote>
    <div class="customer">
