<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>The Problem</h2>



<p>Oberlo wanted to promote their valuable content to site visitors and collect relevant email leads. To do that, they needed a tool that offered full customization and advanced triggers that would enable them to target individual visitors with the right message.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Oberlo didn’t have these options with their previous popup tool, but once they tested Sleeknote, they knew they had found the right tool.</p>



<div style="height:60px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>Turning Visitors into Quality Email Leads</h2>



<p>Oberlo provides access to a large number of eBooks, hubs, and online courses, and they wanted to use this content to build a relevant email list.&nbsp;</p>



<p>One campaign offers a free eBook in exchange for an email address:</p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="694" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8.png" alt="Sleekbox 1" class="wp-image-95466" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8.png 694w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-300x230.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-380x291.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-600x460.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-639x490.png 639w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-220x169.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-385x295.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px" /></figure></div>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>The popup features an illustration of the eBook, which makes it possible for visitors to visualize the value of what they’re getting.</p>



<p>This popup triggers after visitors have been on the site for 10 seconds or if a visitor is about to leave the site. This ensures a better user experience,&nbsp; as visitors get a chance to view the content of the page before getting the offer.&nbsp;</p>



<p>By combining a timed trigger with an exit-intent trigger, Oberlo ensures that every visitor gets a chance to download the eBook before they leave the site.</p>



<p>With this specific campaign, Oberlo collected more than 5,000 unique leads in just 6 days.</p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<div id="testimonial-block_5ec272538bb74" class="block-testimonial">
    <blockquote class="quote">
        “We put a lot of effort into our content to make it unique and useful for our visitors. By promoting this content with Sleeknote, we help visitors find new content and create a better user experience.”    </blockquote>
    <div class="customer">
        <div class="customer-image"><img width="150" height="150" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Siva-copy" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-150x150.jpg 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-300x300.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-380x381.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy.jpg 414w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-35x35.jpg 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-50x50.jpg 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-220x221.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-385x386.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /> </div>        <div class="customer-meta" style="">
            <span class="customer-name">Siva Sankar</span>
            <span class="customer-title">Email Marketing Manager</span>        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<p>Oberlo has also excluded existing subscribers from seeing this popup, as these people have already given their email address once.</p>



<p>Lastly, Oberlo has excluded this popup from showing on their other eBook pages where the call-to-action is different, making sure that it only appears when it’s relevant.</p>



<div style="height:60px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>From Visitor to Subscriber</h2>



<p>Oberlo also uses Sleeknote to collect newsletter permissions on their individual eBook pages:</p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-1024x576.gif" alt="Oberlo-Ebook" class="wp-image-95462" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-1024x576.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-300x169.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-768x432.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-380x214.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-600x338.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-760x428.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-62x35.gif 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-89x50.gif 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-740x416.gif 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-220x124.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Oberlo-Ebook-385x217.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>The popup is triggered with javascript, meaning it doesn’t show unless visitors click the “Download” button.</p>



<p>When visitors click the “Download” button, they don’t know they have to enter their name and email address. And yet, 96.92% of the visitors who did decided to follow-through and provide their details in exchange for the eBook.</p>



<p>That’s impressive, and it’s among the highest conversion rates we’ve ever seen for a campaign like this.&nbsp;</p>



<p>The emails that Oberlo collects are segmented into different email lists based on what kind of eBook they have downloaded. By segmenting leads, Oberlo ensures that leads enter the most relevant email onboarding flow.</p>



<div style="height:60px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>A/B Testing to Find the Best Performing Popup</h2>



<p>To ensure that their campaigns are always optimized, Oberlo does a lot of A/B testing.&nbsp;</p>



<p>They recently created an A/B test to see if a top bar without an eBook offer would outperform their slide-in with the eBook offer.&nbsp;</p>



<p>This is the top bar:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="56" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-1024x56.png" alt="top bar" class="wp-image-95470" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-1024x56.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-300x17.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-768x42.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-380x21.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-600x33.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-760x42.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-180x10.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-250x14.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-740x41.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-220x12.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar-385x21.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/top-bar.png 1088w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>And the slide-in:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="694" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8.png" alt="Sleekbox 1" class="wp-image-95466" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8.png 694w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-300x230.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-380x291.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-600x460.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-639x490.png 639w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-220x169.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Sleekbox-1-8-385x295.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px" /></figure></div>



<p>The results showed that the slide-in with the eBook offer performed 2000% better than the bar, underlining how important it is to offer an incentive in your popups.</p>



<div style="height:60px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2>Favorite Sleeknote Feature</h2>



<p>Siva’s favorite Sleeknote feature is the teaser.</p>



<p>The teaser is a small bar that shows at the bottom of the screen when your popup has yet to be triggered or after it’s been closed. On mobile, the teaser will show first and the popup will only trigger if a visitor clicks to learn more.</p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<div id="testimonial-block_5ec272728bb75" class="block-testimonial">
    <blockquote class="quote">
        “I strongly believe that the teaser is one of the reasons we have such a high conversion rate on our campaigns. It’s a great way to tease the content of the popup in a non-intrusive way. It just works.”    </blockquote>
    <div class="customer">
        <div class="customer-image"><img width="150" height="150" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Siva-copy" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-150x150.jpg 150w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-300x300.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-380x381.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy.jpg 414w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-35x35.jpg 35w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-50x50.jpg 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-220x221.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-385x386.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Siva-copy-120x120.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /> </div>        <div class="customer-meta" style="">
